OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FExtensive low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Fany drizzle slowly lifting, with
OL,7,Fbrighter spells possible during the
OL,8,Fafternoon, especially across eastern
OL,9,Fareas. Increasing chance of showers
OL,10,Fthrough the afternoon, perhaps rather
OL,11,Fheavy. Feeling milder, especially in
OL,12,Fany brightness.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FTurning drier during Monday
OL,15,Fevening with variable cloud amounts.
OL,16,FIsolated showers might continue into
OL,17,Fthe first part of Monday night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
