OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FBreezier through Tuesday,
OL,6,Fwith best of cloud breaks and sunshine
OL,7,Flikely across eastern areas. Perhaps
OL,8,Fremaining damp towards Derbyshire with
OL,9,Fthicker cloud. Chance of rain arriving
OL,10,Fhere in evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FWednesday, early rain clearing, then
OL,14,Fcolder, brighter with blustery
OL,15,Fshowers. Thursday, windy with showers,
OL,16,Fperhaps more persistent rain. Friday
OL,17,Fless windy with sunshine and showers.
OL,18,FTemperatures near normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
